article_id:435,category_name:News,title_name:Issues Regarding Void Battles [Update],image_path:,message:<div>Following some issues with the Void Battles, we have temporarily closed the Wandering Shroom Strike and Obsidian Golem Strike quests.</div><div><br></div><div>■Details of the issues</div><div>・When attempting to play the Wandering Shroom Strike quest, the game gets stuck during the loading screen.</div><div>・In the Obsidian Golem Strike quest, the Obsidian Golem&#39;s attacks don&#39;t deal any damage.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating these issues. Any further updates will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Update <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556173200"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>Corrected a quest name in the &quot;Details of the issues&quot; part of the notice.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Update <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556254800"></span>]</strong></span><br>This issue was fixed at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556254800"></span>.<br>We have therefore reopened the Wandering Shroom Strike and Obsidian Golem Strike quests.<br>Additionally, the Obsidian Golem Strike quest will also be available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556258400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556344799"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556258400"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>As the Obsidian Golem Strike quest was closed while the Limited Void Battle Endeavors were still active, we will extend their active period from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556258400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556863199"></span>.</div><div>Note: The Daily Void Battle Endeavors&#39; active period will not be extended.</div><div><br></div><div>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, the following gifts will be sent to players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556247599"></span>:</div><div><br></div><div>・Quality honey x4</div><div>・Blessed ethon ashes x4</div><div><br></div><div>These gifts can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after logging in.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1556175600,update_time1556267460